      "text": "LocatedatDisney's Typhoon Lagoon Water Park"
    },
    {
      "line": 4,
      "text": "Unwind in your own private shaded area with seating, a flat-screen TV, a mini fridge and more at Disney’s Typhoon Lagoon water park."
    },
