      "line": 10,
      "text": "An Outdoor Sanctuary"
    },
    {
      "line": 11,
      "text": "Renting a Beachcomber Shack is a great way for your group to relax together during your day of fun at Disney’s Typhoon Lagoon water park."
    },
    {
      "line": 12,
      "text": "Each Beachcomber Shack Premium Plus can accommodate up to 10 Guests and includes the following amenities:"
    },
    {
      "line": 13,
      "text": "Cushioned seating for up to 6 Guests"
    },
    {
      "line": 14,
      "text": "A dining table"
    },
    {
      "line": 15,
      "text": "A mini refrigerator"
    },
    {
      "line": 16,
      "text": "A flat-screen TV"
    },
    {
      "line": 17,
      "text": "An oscillating fan"
    },
    {
      "line": 18,
      "text": "Towels"
    },
    {
      "line": 19,
      "text": "A locker"
    },
    {
      "line": 20,
      "text": "Cold water, available all day"
    },
    {
      "line": 21,
      "text": "Electrical outlets"
    },
    {
      "line": 22,
      "text": "Select soft drinks"
    },
    {
      "line": 23,
      "text": "A little more than you need? Consider the Beachcomber Shacks Standard or Beachcomber Shacks Deluxe."
    },
    {
      "line": 24,
      "text": "Dedicated Service"
    },
    {
      "line": 25,
      "text": "Attendants are on hand to help you get the most out of the water park. And when you’re craving a meal or snack, they can take your order for food and beverages (separate dining charges apply)."
